modules.description: This module implements a 2D mesh generator and Delaunay triangulator based on the Triangle library. It provides functions to construct and manipulate planar straight-line graphs (PSLGs), generate triangulations with customizable constraints, and compute Voronoi diagrams. Key operations include triangulate, refine, and copy, which support tasks like finite element meshing, geometric analysis, and mesh adaptation with control over angles, areas, and Steiner points.
